<page>
   <topic>DATE_FORMATS_BUILT_IN Function</topic>
    <description>Date formats for the dtoc() function</description>
 
   <syntax>Format as N = date_formats_built_in()</syntax>
    <discussion>
The DATE_FORMATS_BUILT_IN() function displays the Data Format dialog box and returns the number of the selected format.

   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[? DATE_FORMATS_BUILT_IN()
= "4"]]></example>
   <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
